title: Viral K-Beauty Products That are Actually Worth Your Money #skincare #koreanskincare
description:
We are back with another two products that are actually worth the hype and money 😍 We get that sometimes it might be hard to know which ones are actually up to the hype, and trust us, these ones are!

💓 All available at www.skincupid.co.uk

🤍 MA:NYO Pure Cleansing Oil (200ml):
https://www.skincupid.co.uk/products/ma-nyo-pure-cleansing-oil-200ml

An award-winning cleansing oil that is formulated with 99% naturally-derived nourishing oils to remove impurities, melt blackheads, and unclog the pores for a clear complexion. It balances the skin's pH and delivers ample moisture with a mix of 14 essential oils, whilst removing excess oils and sebum. Packed with antioxidants and soothing oils, this cleansing oil has anti-ageing and calming properties to revitalise the skin and leave it smooth and clear.

🤍IM FROM Rice Toner (150ml):
https://www.skincupid.co.uk/products/im-from-rice-toner-150ml

Made with 77.78% Rice Extract that is naturally rich in antioxidants and vitamins, this toner effectively brightens, improves elasticity, and strengthens the skin barrier by preventing loss of moisture. Meanwhile, this toner also eliminates excess oils and dead skin cells whilst giving the skin large amounts of hydration.
